page.title: 10Games Children Like.
page.content: Most children like{Tiggy}games. The Infant children like games like {'More Girls for Boys Trap'}or'{More {Boys for Girls Trap'.}The Infant boys play,{Knight Rider, A Team,Airwolf, {Fall Guy,Steet Hawk and Space Games. The Infant girls like playing,{Santa {Claus, Mummys and Daddys, Hide and {Seek, Dogs, Birds, Cobra, Skipping and {Trains.}In the 1st year Juniors they play{Transformers,Stuck in the Mud, {Chase,Rainbow Brite,My Little Pony, {Care Bears, Super Heroes,Spiderman,He- {Man,Cars along the wall.}The 3rd and 4th years play{Football }Rugby and harder games.
